<span class="anchor" id="line-1"></span><p class="line867"> <span class="anchor" id="line-2"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-3"></span></p><p class="line867">
</p><h2 id="Ubuntu_Documentation_-_Desktop_Getting_Started">Ubuntu Documentation - Desktop Getting Started</h2>
<span class="anchor" id="line-4"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-5"></span><div><table style="float:right;  font-size:0.9em;  width:42%;  background:#F1F1ED;  margin: 0 0 1em 1em;"><tbody><tr>  <td style="padding:0.5em;"><p class="line891"></p><div class="table-of-contents"><p class="table-of-contents-heading">Contents</p><ol><li>
